title: [Temporal Rift]
description: You are trapped in a time rift!  You catch brief glimpses of events both past and future.  Beyond these strange and confusing visions extends a vast, ever-changing field of stars, pinpoints of light against unfathomable utter blackness.  It is very cold here.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, southeast, south, southwest, west, northwest, up, down
